data.description: Price Improvement!  Beautiful ranch style home in the highly sought after Promontory Subdivision. Built in 2022, this stunning home offers the best of modern living with its thoughtfully designed layout. As you step inside, the open-concept living area creates a warm and welcoming ambiance, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The open kitchen and adjoining dining area are a great focal point for meal prep and enjoying time with family and friends. The primary bedroom with its own bathroom is a serene retreat, offering a seamless blend of comfort and style, making it the perfect place to escape and rejuvenate at the end of each day. Two additional bedrooms on the main floor offer flexibility for a home office or guest rooms, ensuring everyone has their own space. Head downstairs to the partially finished full basement, complete with a fourth bedroom and full bathroom, offering privacy and comfort for guests or extended family members. The basement is a versatile space with endless possibilities to finish to suit your needs. The back yard is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch and landscaping ideas. Create the outdoor oasis of your dreams, whether it's a lush garden retreat or an entertainment area for summer BBQ's. This home's location is a true highlight! Situated near a park with tennis and pickleball courts as well as a baseball field, you'll have endless opportunities for outdoor fun and recreation. Additionally, three fishing ponds nearby offer a tranquil escape for nature enthusiasts. Embrace the Colorado lifestyle with the perfect combination of modern living and outdoor amenities. Schedule your showing today!
